<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 18:08:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队发现加沙战争期间因缺乏装备和条件恶劣而提出的投诉激增 265%</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-finds-spike-in-reservists-complaints-on-lack-of-equipment-poor-conditions/0000018e-2e57-d654-abff-3e57b4b60000</link><description>以色列国防军监察员关于以色列国防军预备役人员投诉的年度报告（主要针对加沙战争时期）发现，有关作战装备、基本防护装备和避难所短缺的投诉大幅增加</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 17:53:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-finds-spike-in-reservists-complaints-on-lack-of-equipment-poor-conditions/0000018e-2e57-d654-abff-3e57b4b60000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 157 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-157/0000018e-2e8d-d12e-ad8e-ee9fca210001</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡称以色列“消灭了哈马斯的四号人物” ■ 美国正试图让加沙战斗停顿 2 至 4 天 ■ 黎巴嫩从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射 15 枚火箭弹 ■ 约旦外交部长：实施限制以色列称耶路撒冷阿克萨清真寺的穆斯林礼拜者正将局势推向“爆炸” ■ 战争结束 157 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 17:39:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-157/0000018e-2e8d-d12e-ad8e-ee9fca210001</guid></item><item><title>以色列决定解散近东救济工程处，但不设立新机构来管理对加沙巴勒斯坦人的援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-dismantle-unrwa-without-replacement-body-to-manage-aid-for-palestinians-in-gaza/0000018e-2e08-dcb3-a58f-ef8d480b0000</link><description>虽然以色列军队计划全面解散联合国机构，以破坏哈马斯在加沙的文官统治，包括通过诽谤活动，但尚不清楚哪个组织将承担其责任</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 16:43:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-dismantle-unrwa-without-replacement-body-to-manage-aid-for-palestinians-in-gaza/0000018e-2e08-dcb3-a58f-ef8d480b0000</guid></item><item><title>入侵加沙会成为一场永无休止的战争吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/could-the-invasion-of-gaza-become-a-never-ending-war/0000018e-2dda-d468-a9ff-2ffb2c690000</link><description>就像俄罗斯在乌克兰的攻势一样，以色列对加沙的入侵可能会成为一场看不到尽头的战争，而且双方无法达成妥协协议来结束战争</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 16:35:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/could-the-invasion-of-gaza-become-a-never-ending-war/0000018e-2dda-d468-a9ff-2ffb2c690000</guid></item><item><title>亲爱的以色列，这是你的朋友乔：拜登必须发表演讲才能让以色列走上和平之路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/dear-people-of-israel-the-speech-biden-must-give-to-set-israel-on-the-path-to-peace/0000018e-2dbd-d2cd-a58f-adfd02bb0000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登必须直接告诉以色列人，他们的未来可能比他们被告知的更加光明。以色列并不孤单，但它最终必须采取措施结束与巴勒斯坦人的恶性现状</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 16:15:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/dear-people-of-israel-the-speech-biden-must-give-to-set-israel-on-the-path-to-peace/0000018e-2dbd-d2cd-a58f-adfd02bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长表示，飞马委员会无视高等法院的命令，要求提供未决案件的详细信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-says-pegasus-commission-asked-for-details-on-pending-cases/0000018e-2de7-d2cd-a58f-ade7fb4b0000</link><description>总检察长加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉 (Gali Baharav-Miara) 告诉最高法院，调查委员会提出的请求违反了法院命令。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 16:01:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-says-pegasus-commission-asked-for-details-on-pending-cases/0000018e-2de7-d2cd-a58f-ade7fb4b0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登的红线：为什么美国可能几天后就会暂停对以色列的武器销售</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/bidens-red-line-why-u-s-could-be-days-away-from-suspending-arms-sales-to-israel/0000018e-2da3-d12e-ad8e-edbb738c0000</link><description>经过几个月的猜测，美国与以色列的关系已经达到了一个转折点，随着美国总统乔·拜登争先恐后地向加沙提供更多人道主义援助，这一时刻可能最终会在本月晚些时候到来。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 15:17:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/bidens-red-line-why-u-s-could-be-days-away-from-suspending-arms-sales-to-israel/0000018e-2da3-d12e-ad8e-edbb738c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列本古里安大学拒绝性别隔离校园以迎合极端正统派的提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-university-rejects-gender-segregation-proposal-for-new-campus/0000018e-2de8-dd22-a5fe-7ffbd2d40000</link><description>尽管该提案的支持者认为，性别隔离的校园将使极端正统派人士能够接受高等教育，但反对者表示，这“违背了平等的价值观”，并有使性别隔离正常化的风险</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 15:06:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-university-rejects-gender-segregation-proposal-for-new-campus/0000018e-2de8-dd22-a5fe-7ffbd2d40000</guid></item><item><title>美国进步团体首次发起针对 AIPAC“黑钱”的此类活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-progressive-groups-launch-first-of-its-kind-campaign-against-aipacs-dark-money/0000018e-2d68-d468-a9ff-2ff9fa510000</link><description>由二十多个进步组织组成的“拒绝 AIPAC”联盟表示，计划通过选举、政治、数字和组织策略来对抗 AIPAC 及其超级 PAC</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 13:09:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-progressive-groups-launch-first-of-its-kind-campaign-against-aipacs-dark-money/0000018e-2d68-d468-a9ff-2ff9fa510000</guid></item><item><title>每逢斋月，以色列犹太人和巴勒斯坦人都会团结起来庆祝这一活动。这次不是</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-03-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ramadan-tours-a-rare-chance-to-unite-jews-and-palestinians-are-cancelled/0000018e-2939-dc52-abff-69bb49240000</link><description>随着加沙战争的激烈进行，“目前还不清楚现在作为游客进入清真寺是否正确，”一位将以色列犹太人和巴勒斯坦人聚集在一起的斋月旅行团的经营者说。但圣月如何成为如此爆炸性的问题呢？</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 13:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-03-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ramadan-tours-a-rare-chance-to-unite-jews-and-palestinians-are-cancelled/0000018e-2939-dc52-abff-69bb49240000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军主席谴责将军未经授权拆除加沙大学大楼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-reprimands-general-for-unauthorized-demolition-of-gaza-university-building/0000018e-2d12-d152-ad8e-2dfa03550000</link><description>以色列军方表示，虽然哈马斯将加沙城的以色列大学大楼用于军事目的，但它是在未经适当授权的情况下被拆除的。 10 月 7 日，希勒姆将军下令炮击贝埃里基布兹的一座房屋，以色列人质被关押在那里，目前正在接受以色列国防军调查</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 12:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-reprimands-general-for-unauthorized-demolition-of-gaza-university-building/0000018e-2d12-d152-ad8e-2dfa03550000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察在斋月的第一个晚上阻止数百名巴勒斯坦人进入阿克萨清真寺，并用警棍殴打信徒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-police-block-hundreds-of-palestinians-from-al-aqsa-on-ramadans-first-night/0000018e-2d17-dc45-a7ef-6ddf8a200000</link><description>对斋月首次祈祷的限制与总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡最近允许礼拜自由的承诺相矛盾。过去几天，警方对巴勒斯坦活动人士和记者发出了数十项限制令，禁止他们进入大院</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 11:18:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-police-block-hundreds-of-palestinians-from-al-aqsa-on-ramadans-first-night/0000018e-2d17-dc45-a7ef-6ddf8a200000</guid></item><item><title>以色列房地产博览会在犹太人聚集的新泽西小镇吸引了数百名亲巴勒斯坦抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-real-estate-fair-draws-hundreds-of-protesters-in-heavily-jewish-n-j-town/0000018e-2cba-d152-ad8e-2dfa9ecd0000</link><description>数百名警察在场，以防止抗议者与犹太居民在活动中发生冲突，该活动在一定程度上促进了西岸的房地产发展</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 11:15:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-real-estate-fair-draws-hundreds-of-protesters-in-heavily-jewish-n-j-town/0000018e-2cba-d152-ad8e-2dfa9ecd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总统赫尔佐格在阿姆斯特丹会见荷兰极右翼反伊斯兰党领袖基尔特·威尔德斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-11/ty-article/israeli-president-meets-dutch-far-right-anti-islam-party-leader-wilders-in-amsterdam/0000018e-2d29-dc45-a7ef-6dfd89610000</link><description>威尔德斯主张荷兰“去伊斯兰化”，主张将荷兰大使馆迁至耶路撒冷并关闭荷兰驻拉马拉外交机构</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 11:10:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-11/ty-article/israeli-president-meets-dutch-far-right-anti-islam-party-leader-wilders-in-amsterdam/0000018e-2d29-dc45-a7ef-6dfd89610000</guid></item><item><title>由于加沙人质与哈马斯的谈判在斋月开始时陷入困境，以色列不排除达成协议的机会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/start-of-ramadan-target-date-for-hostage-deal-arrives-with-no-deal-on-the-horizon/0000018e-2a16-d682-a9df-ebbe83f10000</link><description>一位外国官员表示，双方都在互相较量。另一位人士表示，“我们的假设是最终会达成协议。”哈马斯领导人哈尼亚表示，以色列没有承诺停止战斗并允许流离失所的加沙人从南部返回北部</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:47:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/start-of-ramadan-target-date-for-hostage-deal-arrives-with-no-deal-on-the-horizon/0000018e-2a16-d682-a9df-ebbe83f10000</guid></item><item><title>美国建造的港口可以将以色列变成加沙警察部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/the-american-aid-port-in-gaza-could-turn-idf-into-conquering-and-policing-force/0000018e-2b12-dc45-a7ef-6bdfb5160000</link><description>该港口可能会免除以色列对加沙人道主义局势的责任，但如果没有商定的授权，混乱的风险就会增加</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:47:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/the-american-aid-port-in-gaza-could-turn-idf-into-conquering-and-policing-force/0000018e-2b12-dc45-a7ef-6bdfb5160000</guid></item><item><title>15枚火箭弹从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射；美国向加沙空投援助物资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article-live/gaza-offical-only-hamas-has-the-ability-to-distribute-aid-from-bidens-gaza-port/0000018e-2b4f-dc52-abff-6bcf451b0000</link><description>以色列正在检查哈马斯激进组织二号人物马尔万·伊萨是否在一次袭击中身亡。 据美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 报道，美国相信以色列近期不会在拉法行动。阿克萨大院 ■ 加沙官员警告说，只有哈马斯才有能力监督援助物资的分配 ■ 美国推动战斗暂停两到四天，以恢复协议谈判</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:07:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article-live/gaza-offical-only-hamas-has-the-ability-to-distribute-aid-from-bidens-gaza-port/0000018e-2b4f-dc52-abff-6bcf451b0000</guid></item><item><title>七名阿拉伯裔以色列男子被指控策划对犹太以色列人发动恐怖袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/seven-arab-israeli-men-accused-of-planning-terror-attacks-on-jewish-israelis/0000018e-29fa-dc52-abff-69fa59a70000</link><description>这七人来自北部城市萨赫宁，据称购买武器并接受训练，目的是在战争爆发时攻击犹太公民和士兵。该小组后来由一名自称哈马斯成员的加沙人指挥</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 01:10:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/seven-arab-israeli-men-accused-of-planning-terror-attacks-on-jewish-israelis/0000018e-29fa-dc52-abff-69fa59a70000</guid></item><item><title>2023 年，阿拉伯裔以色列人的谋杀率创下历史新高。今年的步伐正在加快</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arab-murders-on-track-for-another-record-breaking-year/0000018e-29fa-d682-a9df-e9fe43080000</link><description>《国土报》报道称，今年迄今已有 36 名以色列阿拉伯人被谋杀，而 2023 年同期为 31 人，受害者总数为 299 人</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 22:43:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arab-murders-on-track-for-another-record-breaking-year/0000018e-29fa-d682-a9df-e9fe43080000</guid></item><item><title>以色列左翼将在拉马拉宣布胜利，签署两国解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/lefts-victory-photo-will-be-in-muqata/0000018e-2994-d099-a1ff-3bd6d7ed0000</link><description>以色列左派现在有机会提出一种替代刀剑生活的选择，并再次发挥作用</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 21:38:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/lefts-victory-photo-will-be-in-muqata/0000018e-2994-d099-a1ff-3bd6d7ed0000</guid></item></channel></rss>